gw.plugin.billing

Interface BillingAccountInfo


  • public interface BillingAccountInfo
    PolicyCenter shares account information with BillingCenter. There is a one to one mapping between PolicyCenter and BillingCenter accounts.

    The BillingAccountInfo class provides summarized billing information for a given account. See the member list for the details.
